videos.headline: Ragin' Cajun Mitchell scores 64-yard TD
videos.description: QB Andre Nunez dumps it off to Elijah Mitchell, who breaks a couple of tackles and scores a 64-yard touchdown to put Ragin' Cajuns on the board.

videos.headline: Ragin' Cajun Mitchell erupts for a 65-yard TD
videos.description: Elijah Mitchell finds the hole and bursts for a 65-yard touchdown to put the Ragin' Cajuns' back in front 14-7.
